---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "Getting Started with Sun Salutations";
const description = "Learn the fundamental sequence of poses that form the backbone of yoga practice.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">{title}</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
      <p class="lead">
        Sun Salutations (Surya Namaskar) are a flowing sequence of yoga poses that warm up the body and create a moving meditation. This guide will help you get started with this essential practice.
      </p>

      <h2>The Basic Sequence</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Mountain Pose (Tadasana)</li>
        <li>Upward Salute (Urdhva Hastasana)</li>
        <li>Standing Forward Bend (Uttanasana)</li>
        <li>Half Forward Bend (Ardha Uttanasana)</li>
        <li>Plank Pose</li>
        <li>Low Plank or Knees-Chest-Chin</li>
        <li>Cobra or Upward-Facing Dog</li>
        <li>Downward-Facing Dog</li>
      </ol>

      <h2>Benefits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Builds strength and flexibility</li>
        <li>Improves circulation</li>
        <li>Enhances breath awareness</li>
        <li>Creates mental focus</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Practice Tips</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Start with 3-5 rounds</li>
        <li>Move with your breath</li>
        <li>Modify poses as needed</li>
        <li>Practice on an empty stomach</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>